_sText:
Ar_hide_and_seek_house is a port of the hide_and_seek_house20 map from the CSGO game.

The map turned out to be quite large in terms of the size of the output file, despite the fact that the map was initially not very large in size.

A winter forest was carved into the map.

A light version of this map will be released soon.

Description of the map from the author:

This is a map for hide and seek. There are lots of cool hideouts and passages on the map. I tried to make every element on the map perfectly finished the way I wanted. There is one interesting place worth seeing Have fun.
